<%# Enhanced PLC Stage Warning - Point of No Return %>

<div class="plc-danger-zone" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
  <%# CRITICAL WARNING BANNER %>
  <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626 0%, #991b1b 100%); color: white; padding: 24px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.3);">
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
      <span style="font-size: 48px;">üö®</span>
      <div>
        <h2 style="margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800;">POINT OF NO RETURN</h2>
        <p style="margin: 8px 0 0 0; font-size: 16px; opacity: 0.95;">
          The next action will permanently redirect your DID to the new PDS
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15); padding: 16px; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);">
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
        <strong>Once you submit the PLC token:</strong><br>
        ‚Ä¢ Your DID (<code style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;"><%= @migration.did %></code>) will point to <%= @migration.new_pds_host %><br>
        ‚Ä¢ All AT Protocol apps will resolve your identity to the new PDS<br>
        ‚Ä¢ This change is immediate and affects the entire federated network<br>
        ‚Ä¢ <strong>This action CANNOT be undone</strong> without your rotation key
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# WHAT YOU NEED SECTION %>
  <div style="background: #fef3c7; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <h3 style="color: #92400e; margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 18px;">
      üìã What You Need Before Proceeding:
    </h3>
    <ul style="color: #92400e; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; line-height: 1.8;">
      <li><strong>Your rotation key saved securely</strong> (scroll up to copy it)</li>
      <li><strong>Verified all your data migrated</strong> (repository, blobs, preferences)</li>
      <li><strong>The PLC operation token</strong> (will be sent to your email from <%= @migration.old_pds_host %>)</li>
      <li><strong>Understanding this is irreversible</strong> without the rotation key</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <%# INSTRUCTIONS %>
  <div style="background: white; border: 2px solid #e5e7eb; padding: 24px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <h3 style="color: #1f2937; margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 18px;">
      Step-by-Step Instructions:
    </h3>

    <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <div style="display: flex; align-items: start; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, <%= EuroskyConfig::PRIMARY_COLOR %> 0%, <%= EuroskyConfig::SECONDARY_COLOR %> 100%); color: white; width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; flex-shrink: 0;">1</div>
        <div style="flex: 1;">
          <strong style="color: #1f2937; font-size: 15px;">Save Your Rotation Key</strong>
          <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin: 4px 0 0 0;">
            Scroll up and copy your rotation key to a secure location (password manager, encrypted file).
            This is your ONLY way to recover if something goes wrong.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="display: flex; align-items: start; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, <%= EuroskyConfig::PRIMARY_COLOR %> 0%, <%= EuroskyConfig::SECONDARY_COLOR %> 100%); color: white; width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; flex-shrink: 0;">2</div>
        <div style="flex: 1;">
          <strong style="color: #1f2937; font-size: 15px;">Check Your Email</strong>
          <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin: 4px 0 0 0;">
            Your old PDS provider (<strong><%= @migration.old_pds_host %></strong>) has been asked to send you a PLC operation token via email.
            Check your inbox for an email containing the token.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="display: flex; align-items: start; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, <%= EuroskyConfig::PRIMARY_COLOR %> 0%, <%= EuroskyConfig::SECONDARY_COLOR %> 100%); color: white; width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; flex-shrink: 0;">3</div>
        <div style="flex: 1;">
          <strong style="color: #1f2937; font-size: 15px;">Copy the PLC Token</strong>
          <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin: 4px 0 0 0;">
            Copy the PLC operation token from the email sent by your old PDS provider.
            The token will look like a long string of characters.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="display: flex; align-items: start; gap: 12px;">
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, <%= EuroskyConfig::PRIMARY_COLOR %> 0%, <%= EuroskyConfig::SECONDARY_COLOR %> 100%); color: white; width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; flex-shrink: 0;">4</div>
        <div style="flex: 1;">
          <strong style="color: #1f2937; font-size: 15px;">Submit the Token Below</strong>
          <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin: 4px 0 0 0;">
            Paste the PLC token in the form below and submit to complete your migration.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# FINAL WARNING BEFORE FORM %>
  <div style="background: #fee2e2; border: 2px solid #dc2626; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px;">
      <span style="font-size: 32px;">‚ö†Ô∏è</span>
      <h3 style="color: #991b1b; margin: 0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;">
        Final Warning: Are You Ready?
      </h3>
    </div>
    <ul style="color: #991b1b; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; line-height: 1.8;">
      <li>Have you saved your rotation key in a secure location?</li>
      <li>Do you understand this change is permanent and affects the entire AT Protocol network?</li>
      <li>Are you prepared to lose access if you don't have your rotation key?</li>
      <li>Have you verified all your data (posts, media, preferences) migrated successfully?</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="color: #991b1b; font-size: 14px; margin: 12px 0 0 0; font-weight: 600;">
      If you answered NO to any of these questions, DO NOT proceed yet.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
